Doc: The specification of whether a payout will occur on an option depending upon whether the spot rate is at or above or at or below the trigger rate.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The specification of whether a payout will occur on an option depending upon whether the spot rate is at or above or at or below the trigger rate.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.TriggerConditionEnum {
    # The spot rate must be greater than or equal to the trigger rate.
    AtOrAbove 
    # The spot rate must be less than or equal to the trigger rate.
    AtOrBelow 
    # DEPRECATE: The spot rate must be greater than or equal to the trigger rate.
    Above 
    # DEPRECATE: The spot rate must be less than or equal to the trigger rate.
    Below 

}

AtOrAbove.Doc: The spot rate must be greater than or equal to the trigger rate.
AtOrAbove.Name: AtOrAbove

AtOrBelow.Doc: The spot rate must be less than or equal to the trigger rate.
AtOrBelow.Name: AtOrBelow

Above.Doc: DEPRECATE: The spot rate must be greater than or equal to the trigger rate.
Above.Name: Above

Below.Doc: DEPRECATE: The spot rate must be less than or equal to the trigger rate.
Below.Name: Below
